---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import LogoJose from '../components/LogoJose.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Josè Restaurant | Oltre le etichette"
  description="Josè Restaurant: un ritorno alla terra e ai sapori autentici del Vesuvio, oltre le etichette."
  bodyClass="bg-surface text-on-surface selection:bg-terracotta selection:text-white"
>
  <header
    class="fixed top-0 w-full flex justify-between items-center px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop h-20 bg-surface/90 backdrop-blur-md z-50 border-b border-outline-variant/30"
  >
    <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
      <a
        href="/"
        class="flex items-center gap-2 sm:gap-2.5 whitespace-nowrap"
        aria-label="Villa Guerra & Josè — home"
      >
        <span
          class="font-headline-md text-xl sm:text-headline-md text-primary uppercase tracking-widest"
          >Villa Guerra &amp;</span
        >
        <LogoJose class="h-8 sm:h-10 w-auto text-primary" />
      </a>
    </div>
    <nav class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-8">
      <a
        class="text-label-sm font-label-sm text-primary border-b-2 border-antique-gold pb-1"
        href="/jose"
        aria-current="page">Ristorante</a
      >
      <a
        class="text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors"
        href="/tenuta">Eventi</a
      >
      {/* "Cantina" nascosta dal nav su richiesta: la pagina /cantina resta online ma non linkata — togliere il commento alla riga sotto per rimostrarla. "Storia" rimossa: nessun contenuto. */}
      {/* <a class="text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="/cantina">Cantina</a> */}
    </nav>
    <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
      <a
        href="#contatti"
        class="hidden sm:inline-block bg-terracotta text-lava-stone px-6 py-2 font-label-sm text-label-sm font-bold hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity"
        >Prenota Ora</a
      >
      <button
        id="menu-toggle"
        class="md:hidden material-symbols-outlined text-primary cursor-pointer leading-none"
        aria-label="Apri menu"
        aria-controls="mobile-menu"
        aria-expanded="false"
        >menu</button
      >
    </div>

    <!-- Menu mobile -->
    <div
      id="mobile-menu"
      class="md:hidden fixed top-20 left-0 w-full bg-surface/95 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-outline-variant/30 z-40 hidden flex-col px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop py-6 gap-1 shadow-lg"
    >
      <a
        class="text-label-sm font-label-sm text-primary py-3 border-b border-outline-variant/20"
        href="/jose"
        aria-current="page">Ristorante</a
      >
      <a
        class="text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant py-3 border-b border-outline-variant/20"
        href="/tenuta">Eventi</a
      >
      {/* "Cantina" e "Storia" nascoste anche dal menu mobile (vedi nav desktop). */}
      {/* <a class="text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant py-3 border-b border-outline-variant/20" href="/cantina">Cantina</a> */}
      <a
        href="#contatti"
        class="mt-4 bg-terracotta text-lava-stone px-6 py-3 text-center font-label-sm text-label-sm font-bold hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity"
        >Prenota Ora</a
      >
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="pt-20">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="relative h-[90vh] overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0">
        <img
          alt="Spaghetti gourmet ai frutti di mare di Josè Restaurant"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          src="/images/jose-hero-gourmet.jpg"
        />
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-lava-stone via-lava-stone/70 via-35% to-transparent to-70%"
        >
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="relative h-full flex flex-col items-center justify-end pb-32 px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop text-center"
      >
        <h1
          class="font-headline-display text-[2.25rem] sm:text-5xl md:text-headline-display text-silk-white max-w-4xl mb-6 break-words"
        >
          Oltre le etichette, verso l'autenticità
        </h1>
        <p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-silk-white/90 max-w-2xl">
          Un ritorno alla terra, ai sapori nudi del Vesuvio, liberati dai
          formalismi per riscoprire l'anima vera dell'ospitalità campana.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-12 animate-bounce">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-silk-white text-4xl"
            >keyboard_double_arrow_down</span
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Manifesto -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-surface px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop">
      <div
        class="max-w-container-max mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-24 items-center"
      >
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <span
            class="text-label-sm font-label-sm text-vesuvius-green tracking-widest uppercase"
            >Il Nostro Manifesto</span
          >
          <div
            class="font-headline-lg text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-headline-lg text-on-surface leading-tight break-words"
          >
            La cucina è un atto di resistenza contro la standardizzazione del
            gusto.
          </div>
          <div
            class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant space-y-6"
          >
            <p>
              A Josè Restaurant, abbiamo scelto di spogliarci delle
              sovrastrutture. Non cerchiamo la perfezione geometrica nel piatto,
              ma la vibrazione del sapore che nasce quando un ingrediente
              incontra la mano di chi lo rispetta.
            </p>
            <p>
              Il Vesuvio non è solo uno sfondo, è l'ingrediente segreto: la
              pietra lavica che trattiene il sole, la cenere che nutre le
              radici, l'aria salmastra che scivola giù dal cratere. Ogni boccone
              è una geologia del gusto, un ritorno a casa senza passare per vie
              già battute.
            </p>
          </div>
          <a
            href="#menu"
            class="group inline-flex items-center gap-3 text-primary font-bold"
          >
            <span class="font-label-sm text-label-sm uppercase">Sfoglia la carta</span>
            <span
              class="material-symbols-outlined transition-transform duration-300 ease-out group-hover:translate-x-1"
              >east</span
            >
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="aspect-[4/5] bg-vesuvius-green overflow-hidden">
            <div
              id="proposta-carousel"
              class="flex h-full w-full overflow-x-auto snap-x snap-mandatory no-scrollbar"
              aria-roledescription="carosello"
              aria-label="I piatti di cucina di Josè Restaurant"
              tabindex="0"
            >
              <img
                class="snap-center shrink-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
                src="/images/jose-piatto-3.jpg"
                alt="Piatto gourmet di mare di Josè Restaurant"
                loading="lazy"
              />
              <img
                class="snap-center shrink-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
                src="/images/jose-pasta-mare.jpg"
                alt="Pasta con frutti di mare di Josè Restaurant"
                loading="lazy"
              />
              <img
                class="snap-center shrink-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
                src="/images/jose-piatto-2.jpg"
                alt="Pasta fresca della carta di Josè Restaurant"
                loading="lazy"
              />
              <img
                class="snap-center shrink-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
                src="/images/jose-piatto-4.jpg"
                alt="Creazione dello chef impiattata"
                loading="lazy"
              />
            </div>
            <!-- controlli carosello -->
            <div class="absolute bottom-4 right-4 z-10 flex items-center gap-3">
              <div
                class="proposta-dots flex items-center gap-1.5"
                role="tablist"
                aria-label="Vai al piatto"
              >
              </div>
              <div class="flex gap-2">
                <button
                  type="button"
                  data-carousel="prev"
                  aria-label="Piatto precedente"
                  class="grid place-items-center h-9 w-9 bg-lava-stone/70 backdrop-blur-sm text-silk-white hover:bg-terracotta hover:text-lava-stone transition-colors focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-silk-white"
                >
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[20px] leading-none">chevron_left</span>
                </button>
                <button
                  type="button"
                  data-carousel="next"
                  aria-label="Piatto successivo"
                  class="grid place-items-center h-9 w-9 bg-lava-stone/70 backdrop-blur-sm text-silk-white hover:bg-terracotta hover:text-lava-stone transition-colors focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-silk-white"
                >
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[20px] leading-none">chevron_right</span>
                </button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-12 -left-12 bg-terracotta p-12 hidden md:block z-20 pointer-events-none">
            <span class="text-lava-stone font-headline-md text-headline-md italic"
              >«Il sapore non mente mai.»</span
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Pizzeria -->
    <section
      id="pizzeria"
      class="py-24 bg-surface-container px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop scroll-mt-20"
    >
      <div
        class="max-w-container-max mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-24 items-center"
      >
        <!-- Carosello pizze -->
        <div class="relative order-2 lg:order-1">
          <div class="aspect-[4/5] bg-lava-stone overflow-hidden">
            <div
              id="pizzeria-carousel"
              class="flex h-full w-full overflow-x-auto snap-x snap-mandatory no-scrollbar"
              aria-roledescription="carosello"
              aria-label="Le pizze di Josè"
              tabindex="0"
            >
              <img
                class="snap-center shrink-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
                src="/images/jose-pizza-margherita.jpg"
                alt="Pizza margherita con basilico e pomodorini dal forno a legna di Josè"
                loading="lazy"
              />
              <img
                class="snap-center shrink-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
                src="/images/jose-pizza-fiori.jpg"
                alt="Pizza con fiori di zucca e crema di pesto di Josè Restaurant"
                loading="lazy"
              />
              <img
                class="snap-center shrink-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
                src="/images/jose-pizza-salmone.jpg"
                alt="Pizza con salmone, insalata e pomodorini di Josè Restaurant"
                loading="lazy"
              />
              <img
                class="snap-center shrink-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
                src="/images/jose-pizza.jpg"
                alt="Pizza gourmet dal forno a legna di Josè Restaurant"
                loading="lazy"
              />
              <img
                class="snap-center shrink-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
                src="/images/jose-forno-fiamme.jpg"
                alt="Pizze in cottura nel forno a legna acceso di Josè"
                loading="lazy"
              />
              <img
                class="snap-center shrink-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
                src="/images/jose-forno-servizio.jpg"
                alt="Gli chef di Josè servono le pizze appena sfornate"
                loading="lazy"
              />
            </div>
            <!-- controlli carosello -->
            <div class="absolute bottom-4 right-4 z-10 flex items-center gap-3">
              <div
                class="pizzeria-dots flex items-center gap-1.5"
                role="tablist"
                aria-label="Vai alla pizza"
              >
              </div>
              <div class="flex gap-2">
                <button
                  type="button"
                  data-carousel="prev"
                  aria-label="Pizza precedente"
                  class="grid place-items-center h-9 w-9 bg-lava-stone/70 backdrop-blur-sm text-silk-white hover:bg-terracotta hover:text-lava-stone transition-colors focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-silk-white"
                >
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[20px] leading-none">chevron_left</span>
                </button>
                <button
                  type="button"
                  data-carousel="next"
                  aria-label="Pizza successiva"
                  class="grid place-items-center h-9 w-9 bg-lava-stone/70 backdrop-blur-sm text-silk-white hover:bg-terracotta hover:text-lava-stone transition-colors focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-silk-white"
                >
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[20px] leading-none">chevron_right</span>
                </button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Testo pizzeria -->
        <div class="space-y-8 order-1 lg:order-2">
          <span
            class="text-label-sm font-label-sm text-terracotta tracking-widest uppercase"
            >Pizzeria · Casual · Aprile – Settembre</span
          >
          <div
            class="font-headline-lg text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-headline-lg text-on-surface leading-tight break-words"
          >
            La Pizza in Giardino
          </div>
          <div class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant space-y-6">
            <p>
              Accanto alla cucina, una proposta più informale: pizze gourmet con
              farine selezionate, lievitazioni lente e ingredienti del
              territorio, cotte nel forno a legna.
            </p>
            <p>
              Le serviamo nell'atmosfera rilassata dei giardini della Villa, da
              aprile a settembre, quando il Vesuvio si gode all'aperto.
            </p>
          </div>
          <a
            href="#contatti"
            class="group inline-flex items-center gap-3 text-primary font-bold"
          >
            <span class="font-label-sm text-label-sm uppercase">Prenota un tavolo</span>
            <span
              class="material-symbols-outlined transition-transform duration-300 ease-out group-hover:translate-x-1"
              >east</span
            >
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- La Proposta -->
    <section class="bg-lava-stone py-24 px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop overflow-hidden">
      <div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto">
        <div class="max-w-xl mb-16">
          <h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-silk-white mb-4">
            La Proposta
          </h2>
          <p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-surface-variant">
            Un dialogo stagionale tra orto e mare, dove ogni ricetta è un
            frammento di storia vesuviana reinterpretata con occhi
            contemporanei.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-gutter">
          <div class="group relative aspect-square overflow-hidden">
            <img
              alt="Piatto di stagione con le verdure dell'orto vulcanico"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-105"
              src="/images/jose-orto.jpg"
            />
            <div
              class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/75 via-black/20 to-transparent flex flex-col justify-end p-8"
            >
              <h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-silk-white">
                L'Orto Vulcanico
              </h3>
              <p class="text-surface-variant font-body-md">
                Stagionalità cruda e autentica.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div
            class="group relative aspect-square overflow-hidden bg-terracotta/20"
          >
            <img
              alt="Piatto gourmet: l'evoluzione contemporanea della tradizione"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-105"
              src="/images/jose-gourmet.jpg"
            />
            <div
              class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/75 via-black/20 to-transparent flex flex-col justify-end p-8"
            >
              <h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-silk-white">
                Visioni Contemporanee
              </h3>
              <p class="text-surface-variant font-body-md">
                L'evoluzione della tradizione.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="group relative aspect-square overflow-hidden">
            <img
              alt="Tavola apparecchiata con i vini del territorio vesuviano"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-105"
              src="/images/jose-vini.jpg"
            />
            <div
              class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/75 via-black/20 to-transparent flex flex-col justify-end p-8"
            >
              <h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-silk-white">
                Vini dal Cratere
              </h3>
              <p class="text-surface-variant font-body-md">
                Etichette eroiche e territoriali.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- La Carta / Menù -->
    <section
      id="menu"
      class="py-24 md:py-28 px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop bg-surface scroll-mt-20"
    >
      <div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto">
        <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center mb-14">
          <h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-on-surface leading-tight">
            La Carta
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-4 font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant">
            Il menù è stagionale e cambia con quello che la terra e il mare
            offrono. I prezzi indicati sono per portata, sulla carta del
            momento.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto space-y-16">
          <!-- Antipasti -->
          <div>
            <div
              class="flex items-baseline justify-center gap-4 border-b border-outline-variant/50 pb-3 mb-6"
            >
              <h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-primary">Antipasti</h3>
              <span
                class="font-label-sm text-label-sm text-terracotta whitespace-nowrap"
                >€16 – 20</span
              >
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-5 text-center">
              <li class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface leading-snug">
                Scarola imbottita, alici del Cantabrico e spuma di fagioli
                tondini
              </li>
              <li class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface leading-snug">
                Millefoglie di melanzane in parmigiana<span
                  class="text-on-surface-variant italic"
                >
                  · tradizione pura</span
                >
              </li>
              <li class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface leading-snug">
                Carpaccio di tonno rosso e bruschetta al pomodoro
              </li>
              <li class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface leading-snug">
                Tagliatella di seppia con variazione di zucchine alla scapece
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Primi -->
          <div>
            <div
              class="flex items-baseline justify-center gap-4 border-b border-outline-variant/50 pb-3 mb-6"
            >
              <h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-primary">
                Primi Piatti
              </h3>
              <span
                class="font-label-sm text-label-sm text-terracotta whitespace-nowrap"
                >€18 – 26</span
              >
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-5 text-center">
              <li class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface leading-snug">
                Taglioni all'uovo alla Nerano<span
                  class="text-on-surface-variant italic"
                >
                  · il classico intramontabile</span
                >
              </li>
              <li class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface leading-snug">
                Chicche di patate con piselli, scampi e tartufo nero
              </li>
              <li class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface leading-snug">
                Minestra di pasta, riccio di mare, patelle e sconcigli
              </li>
              <li class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface leading-snug">
                Risotto con astice e sfusato amalfitano<span
                  class="text-on-surface-variant italic"
                >
                  · min. 2 persone</span
                >
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Secondi -->
          <div>
            <div
              class="flex items-baseline justify-center gap-4 border-b border-outline-variant/50 pb-3 mb-6"
            >
              <h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-primary">
                Secondi Piatti
              </h3>
              <span
                class="font-label-sm text-label-sm text-terracotta whitespace-nowrap"
                >€20 – 35</span
              >
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-5 text-center">
              <li class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface leading-snug">
                Maiale nero in lenta cottura con taccole alla pizzaiola
              </li>
              <li class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface leading-snug">
                Entrecôte alla griglia con rucola e funghi cardoncelli
              </li>
              <li class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface leading-snug">
                Baccalà fritto con salsa alla «bella donna»
              </li>
              <li class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface leading-snug">
                Fritto di gamberi e calamari freschi
              </li>
              <li class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface leading-snug">
                Misto di pesce alla griglia con verdurine al salto
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Prenotazione -->
    <section id="contatti" class="py-24 px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop bg-surface-container">
      <div
        class="max-w-[1000px] mx-auto bg-white shadow-2xl overflow-hidden flex flex-col md:flex-row"
      >
        <div
          class="md:w-1/2 bg-vesuvius-green p-12 text-silk-white flex flex-col justify-between"
        >
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg mb-6">
              Prenota la tua esperienza
            </h2>
            <p class="font-body-md text-body-md opacity-80">
              Assicurati un tavolo a Josè Restaurant. Lasciati guidare
              attraverso un percorso dove il tempo si ferma e il sapore diventa
              protagonista.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-12 space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-terracotta">phone</span>
              <span class="font-label-sm text-label-sm">+39 081 123 4567</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-terracotta"
                >location_on</span
              >
              <span class="font-label-sm text-label-sm"
                >Via Villa Guerra, 7 - Torre del Greco (NA)</span
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-1/2 p-12 bg-silk-white">
          <form class="space-y-6">
            <div>
              <label
                for="pren-data"
                class="block text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant mb-2"
                >Data</label
              >
              <input
                id="pren-data"
                name="data"
                type="date"
                required
                class="w-full border-b border-outline-variant bg-transparent py-2 focus:ring-0 focus:border-vesuvius-green focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-4 focus-visible:outline-vesuvius-green transition-colors"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-gutter">
              <div>
                <label
                  for="pren-persone"
